What "appropriate credit" means here
------------------------------------

If you fork, redistribute, embed, or build a derivative of this project,
keep the "Made by @sandeep" attribution visible somewhere in the
end-user-facing product. The bottom-right credit pill on the landing
page is the canonical placement; a line in your README or About page
also works. Don't hide it, don't strip it, don't replace it.

That's it. No additional restrictions. No warranty.
